{"id":298621,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/06/冯学荣-《川岛芳子到底死了没有？》/","date":"2013-06-12T06:39:07Z","modified":"2013-06-12T06:39:07Z","title":"冯学荣 | 《川岛芳子到底死了没有？》","content":"<p><p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">《川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子到底死了没有？》</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p ALIGN=\"center\">\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">冯</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">学荣</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">关于川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子（金</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">壁辉</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">）到底是被国府</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">枪毙</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">了，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">还</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">是被私下</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">释</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">放了，笔者依据自己所接触到的一些</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">人</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">言，也来一个分析。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">首先，我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">看看川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">亲</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">哥哥</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">爱</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">新</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">觉罗</span><span>·</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">宪</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">均的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">言：</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span>“</span><span>河北省高等法院于</span><span>1948</span><span>年</span><span>3</span><span>月</span><span>25</span><span>日凌晨，将</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">金壁</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">辉枪</span><span>决了，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">她</span><span>的尸体由她在北平的十姐</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">爱</span><span>新</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">觉罗</span><span>.</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">显狮</span><span>和日本僧人古川大航</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">领</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">走</span><span>并且火化了。</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">金壁</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">辉</span><span>的尸体被火化</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">之</span><span>后，她的骨灰一半送去了日本，一半</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">则</span><span>留在了中国</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">。</span><span>”</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子哥哥的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">这</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">份</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">言，收</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">录</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">在</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">《文史</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">资</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">料</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">选编</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">》第</span><span>23</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">辑《金壁辉其人》一文当中。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">可见，作为川岛芳子的亲生哥哥，宪均认为：川岛芳子的确被国府枪决了。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">再来看看台湾那</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">边</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的国民政府</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">狱</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">政档案。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span>时任北平第一监狱典狱长</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span>吴峙沅</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">在台湾的狱政档案中，留下了这样的记录</span><span>:</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span>“</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">（川岛芳子）</span><span>执行死刑并经何承斌检察官验明正身，讯留遗书后，命令法警执行一枪毙命，事后经检察官率同检验员三次覆验，确已死亡，始将尸体交由本监移出非常门外停放，以备各新闻记者参观暨拍照，同日午后并准由日僧古川大航具领掩埋</span><span>”</span><span>。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">这份资料，出自于台湾当局</span><span>法务部编纂完成的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">《</span><span>百年狱政档案</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">》中。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">读者可以看到：台湾方面的狱政档案，和大陆这边的宪均（川岛芳子的亲哥哥）的证言是吻合的，即：川岛芳子不但的确被枪决了，而且尸体是由日本僧人</span><span>古川大航</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">领走了。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">我们再来看看川岛芳子的亲妹妹、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%82%83%E4%BA%B2%E7%8E%8B\"><span>肃亲王</span></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%96%84%E8%80%86\"><span>善耆</span></a></span><span>的第</span><span>38</span><span>个孩子</span><span>金默玉</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">言。</span><span>2008</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span>11</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>19</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">日，在</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">东</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">北</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">调查</span><span>“</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子没死</span><span>”</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">传闻</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">记</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">者，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">电话</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">采</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">访</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">了身在廊坊</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的</span><span>金默玉，金默玉</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">是</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">这样说</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">的：</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span>“</span><span>当年她（川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span>芳子）被</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">枪</span><span>决</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">时</span><span>，也有被替身</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">赎</span><span>出的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">传</span><span>言，我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们</span><span>看了行刑后的照片，那是她本人，没有</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">假</span><span>的，你</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们现</span><span>在听到的都是</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">谣</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">言</span><span>。</span><span>”</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">于是我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们进</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">一步知道，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">不但川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">亲</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">哥哥</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">宪</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">均深信川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子已</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">经被国府枪决</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">身亡，川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">亲</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">妹妹</span><span>金默玉</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">也</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">认为</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子的确已</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">经</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">被国府</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">枪</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">决身亡。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">这还没完，大家再跟笔者来看看当年亲眼目睹枪决川岛芳子的国民党老兵谭良泽老先生的证言。谭良泽老先生是原</span><span>国民党</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">宪</span><span>兵</span><span>19</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">团驻</span><span>西区</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">宪</span><span>兵</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">队</span><span>少校主官</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">当年负责枪毙川岛芳子的刑场警戒任务。</span><span>2004</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">年，谭良泽老先生在四川自贡接受媒体采访，是这样说的：</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span>“</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">川</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">岛</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">芳子被</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">处</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">决是</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">铁的事实，之所以传出未死的谣言，是因为此次处决的开抢过程没有允许记者公开目击，所以引起了记者不满所致。</span><span>”</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">谭良泽老先生作为目击者，他的这篇证言采访文章，名叫《帝国谍报之花的末日：处决川岛芳子的全过程》。有兴趣的读者可以找来一读。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">还</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">有一个目</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">击证</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">人，他就是当年《北平</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">时报</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">》的</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">记</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">者</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">许</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">杏林，他在</span><span>2004</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">年接受《城市快</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">报</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">》</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">记</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">者黄</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">卫采访时，是这样说的：</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span> “</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">行刑</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">时</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">不准我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们记者进去看，我们被挡在大门外，听到了枪声，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">到七点左右，</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">监狱</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">打开大</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">门</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">放我</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">们进</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">去，在</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">狱警的带领下来到监狱内的刑场一看，只见一具女尸，装在木匣子里，子弹从前额射出，由于使用的是开花弹，面部血肉模糊，已经无法辨认，因此，从此社会上就出现了种种猜测和传闻。</span><span>”</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">许杏林老先生作为目击者，他的这篇证言采访文章，名叫《我听到了击毙川岛芳子的枪声》。有兴趣的读者可以找来一读。</span></p>\n<p>\n<span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">材料我就</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">暂时举到这里，有空再详谈，不过我相信诸位看官应该可以判断个七七八八了。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">质疑川岛芳子的死，没有问题，但是，任何假设的证实，都是需要确凿证据的。</span></p>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<div>\n<span> </span>\n</div>\n<p>\n<span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">冯学荣。</span><span>2013</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span>6</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>10</span><span LANG=\"ZH-CN\">日。写于美国三藩市。</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://simg.sinajs.cn/blog7style/images/special/1265.gif\" /> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469641,474922&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473458&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http://qing.blog.sina.com.cn/tag/%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F\">青春就应该这样绽放</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469645,474926&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473464&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Funion.9173.com%2Fpub%3Fp%3D1%26u%3D1008\">游戏测试：三国时期谁是你最好的兄弟！！</a>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://sina.allyes.com/main/adfclick?db=sina&#038;bid=204720,469646,474927&#038;cid=0,0,0&#038;sid=473465&#038;advid=358&#038;camid=37389&#038;show=ignore&#038;url=http